)BODY Expand(//)
%Tutorial /-/  EDIT  /-/ Tutorial
%COMMAND ===>_ZCMD                                                             +
+
%                     -----------------------------------
                      |      Edit Macro  "FLOWJCL"      |
                      -----------------------------------
+
%FUNCTION  :+This Edit macro allows all the JCL DD statements to be reformatted
             with one parameter by line.
%OPERATION :+starting at the top of the data, all DD statements are reformatted
             by beeing copied one parameter at a time (new lines are inserted
             into the data to contain all the reformatted DD statements).
             Anything other than part of a DD statement is left as is.
%SYNTAX :+      FLOWJCL
                FLOWJCL HELP or H
+
)PROC
  &ZCONT = PAJTFLWJ
)END
